title: Estadio José María Olaeta
text: Estadio José Martin Olaeta is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Rosario%2C%20Santa%20Fe">Rosario</a>, <a href="Argentina">Argentina</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Argentino%20de%20Rosario">Argentino de Rosario</a>. The stadium holds 6,800 people.
